g": null, "text": "可以不存学费，直接开学就行，有人会搞这个", "timestamp": 1629212886, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300865, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": 2300681, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 哦豁。谢谢!", "timestamp": 1629214051, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300963, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz本科入学时是先交了学费，之后贷款打给学校后退到了中行卡上", "timestamp": 1629214622, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301291, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "保证银行卡里的钱小于你的学费，不然会被自动扣款。你贷款的时候不是有个小单子让你交给学校吗？开学的时候交了就行", "timestamp": 1629217136, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301319, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": 2301291, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 明白了 谢谢!", "timestamp": 1629217443, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301328, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": 2300963, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我明天再去问问老师....", "timestamp": 1629217469, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301475, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "卡里别留那么多钱就行，都是贷款哪来那么多钱是不（不是", "timestamp": 1629218327, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301491, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": 2301475, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 卡里么的钱😂😂就一块钱", "timestamp": 1629218444, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301584, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": 2301491, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那就没事，不用急，学校不会少了你的钱😂", "timestamp": 1629219315, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2310514, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": 2300681, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: info是什么意思呀", "timestamp": 1629336961, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2311350, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "层主你也收到的是一个验证码？然后去高校录入回执", "timestamp": 1629346369, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2316849, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": 2310514, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 就是thu的信息网? 如果是新生的话，不用着急，等报到把回执单给学校就好(应该)", "timestamp": 1629390009, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2318059, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": 2316849, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 洞主你打算怎么办？我觉得先交了学费还蛮稳妥的", "timestamp": 1629419575, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2318792, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": 2318059, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 我给老师打了个电话，老师说这几天会有通知，会统计贷款的学生，没事的", "timestamp": 1629428738, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2319059, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 441788, "reply_to": 2318792, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 好的多谢", "timestamp": 1629431466, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 441788, "reply": 23, "tag": null, "text": "目前dz已经申请下来生源地助学贷款了，想问问，如何与学校取得联系啊，就是告知学校:我目前不交学费，需要等待贷款。  非清本研究生很慌，怕自己因为没交费放弃录取资格。", "timestamp": 1629212315, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629431467, "url": "", "vote": {}}}